    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Textile fabric having a very long, soft pile, which may imitate fur, made of plant fiber or synthetic fiber. The textile may occur in any color, not necessarily resembling the coat of a mammal, and is typically used for fashion and interior decoration.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
